  "texts": [
    "Our multi-shot method yields a helpfulness score distribution that is shifted further to the right; for the safety, it not only generates more responses with high scores near 20 but also reduces the number of highly unsafe responses with very low scores below -20.",
    "We defer additional experimental results to Appendix D.1.",
    "Multi-constraint resultWe demonstrate that our iterative dual-based method satisfies two constraints while maximizing the primary reward in the multi-constraint task.Constraint satisfaction.",
    "Figure 2a shows the expected versus actual improvements for 14 combinations of harmlessness and humor constraints.",
    "We observe that both the harmlessness and humor constraints are generally satisfied, with the results lying close to the reference lines, demonstrating the effectiveness of our method to satisfy multiple constraints."
